                        <h3>Review Proposals</h3>
                        <p>Receive proposals from qualified freelancers and review their profiles and portfolios.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="step-number">03</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Hire the Best Match</h3>
                        <p>Select the freelancer who best fits your project needs and budget.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
